Date: 16 Feb 2003
From: Stephen M. Apatow <s.m.apatow@humanitarian.net>

Have they ruled out END? (Exotic Newcastle Disease)
Virulence of Pigeon-Origin Newcastle Disease Virus Isolates for Domestic
Chickens: USDA:ARS
<http://www.nps.ars.usda.gov/publications/publications.htm?SEQ_NO_115=121102>
